## **1. Clean, Direct, Public‑Safe**
Royal Rebirth Bank is a privately organized unincorporated association that functions as a mixed holding structure supporting internal financial, administrative, and operational activities across its associated entities. It serves as the Issuer of the Royal Rebirth Stable Coin within the Estate & Trust Private Wealth Architecture.

